  <summary date="2019-12-18T21:12:48Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Safety Over Arbitration Act of 2019

This bill limits the use of mandatory arbitration agreements in disputes involving a hazard to public health or safety.

Specifically, the bill prohibits the use of arbitration to resolve such a dispute unless all parties agree to arbitration in writing after the dispute arises.</summary>
